class Foo(Struct):
    byte = u8
    twobytes = u16
    fourbytes = u32
    eightbytes = u64
f = Foo()
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    f.byte = 256
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    f.twobytes = 65536
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    f.fourbytes = 4294967296
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    f.eightbytes = 18446744073709551616
